QuestData.Title: Adventurers Wanted: Blackfathom Deeps
QuestData.Description: King Anduin Wrynn has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Blackfathom Deeps, west of Astranaar, immediately!$B$BThe Twilight's Hammer threatens the world with its actions there! If you so choose, head to Blackfathom Deeps and speak with Sentinel Aluwyn, head of the night elf effort there, to help stop the Twilight threat.
